{"tid":1851981,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣人真幸福啊！ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-01-30T08:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:02:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5070d676982fc8ddac799d8f23a02d08c41e883","tid":1851981,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200130/20852474/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200130%2F20852474%2F&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=f1b8f598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200130%2F20852474%2F&h=4d3be56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200130/20852474/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣人真幸福啊！ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200130/large/1580281390_1a6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200130%2Flarge%2F1580281390_1a6e.jpg&h=ed1572f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上截圖<br />\n<br />\n中國瘟疫蔓延，香港政府不採取任何防疫措施，基本上是歡迎瘟疫病人湧港，不介意香港變成疫埠。其動機相當可疑。後來，雖然終於宣佈禁止來自武漢的航班及高鐵入境，但港珠澳大橋仍免費開放，各大陸路關口亦暢通無阻。是疏忽還是別有用心，大家自行揣測。一個毫無民意認受性的政府，根本不必向民眾交代。<br />\n<br />\n看看一人一票選總統的台灣如何防疫，發現第一宗確診個案後，台灣政府迅速宣佈禁止所有武漢旅客入境。確診第二例、第三例後，更將禁令擴大至湖北省。由於第二例確診病人為中國赴台旅遊團遊客，台灣政府立即暫停所有已在台灣的10個湖北旅遊團的行程，要求他們盡速離境。<br />\n<br />\n所有入境台灣人士均須如實填寫健康申報表，若被發現不實，是有罰則的。其中一個被確診台商未如實申報，被罰款30萬台幣。<br />\n<br />\n此外，台灣政府宣佈口罩不出口之後，雖然受到藍營人士攻擊，但行政院長蘇貞昌擲地有聲地回應，先要自救，才可以幫人。這才是一個負責任的政府所為。<br />\n<br />\n中國瘟疫大爆發之前，台灣剛剛經過總統大選，台灣人用自己的智慧選出了蔡英文，蔡英文承諾「留下一個更好的國家」。事實證明，台灣人的選擇是正確的，蔡英文面對的第一個挑戰便是世紀大瘟疫，她所領導的政府，迅速、決斷，以台灣人的福祉為最大考量，真令人羨慕！台灣人真幸福啊！ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"7a38583c4fea6618c1b832b463ccc769b1402dd6","tid":1851981,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=0576379c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"0349a2b7dc008e3d44cee7491551da209109052f","tid":1851981,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"人地陳水扁食子彈時港畜仲笑緊人地黑金政治劣質民主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}